    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in showroom condition and babied since day one. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014not a scratch or a speck of dust to be found! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
