      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality specimen that has been meticulously preserved since day one. This vehicle boasts a flawless factory finish with a deep, glass-like luster, completely free from road rash, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery retains its original scent and supple texture, with absolutely zero wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic component and switch functions with the crisp tactile feedback of a new car. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, document-backed service history and a powertrain that operates with surgical precision. Always garage-kept under a climate-controlled cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its class for the discerning collector who demands perfection.",
